name: Space Warrior ANA 5: ARTIFICIAL GOD COMPLEX
name_original: Space Warrior ANA 5: ARTIFICIAL GOD COMPLEX
description:
Ana and her friends (and enemies) are back with another sequel! It's up to them to save the citizens of the universe from being converted into robots.

>6 playable characters!

>8 stages full of robots, monsters, and cute girls!

>9 unique and fun bosses!

>An awesome electronic soundtrack!

>A short, yet compelling story!

### Controls ###

Arrow Keys: Move

Z: Toggle fire

X: Bomb

Shift: Focus (This causes you the move slowly and reveals your hitbox)

R: Reset (This causes you to instantly lose all HP, and get a Game Over)

ESC: Pause

This game contains flashing lights and may not be suitable for those who are sensitive to them.
